com.capitalone.dashboard.collector

Class CollectorTask<T extends Collector>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.capitalone.dashboard.collector.CollectorTask<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Class that extends Collector
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CollectorTaskWithGenericItem

    @Component
public abstract class CollectorTask<T extends Collector>
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Base class for Collector task implementation which provides subclasses with the following:

    1. Creates a Collector instance the first time the collector runs.
    2. Uses TaskScheduler to schedule the job based on the provided cron when the process starts.
    3. Saves the last execution time on the collector when the collection run finishes.
    4. Sets the collector online/offline when the collector process starts/stops
